ior. The absolute worst group I was ever in was all female except for me. Either way, yeah, no secret as to the sexual leanings of the game designers. If you doubt that, walk up to a barb female as a human character. Got to look up to see her face. Otherwise your gaze rests squarely in a zone that would cause trouble in real life. Best advice I can give is to stay away from the sexual stuff and stick with making a friend regardless of whether they're male or female. Never know when they might be wandering by when you're in trouble and save your butt.  <BR>  <BR>  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><br><font color=#333399>- </font><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthedruidsgrove>The Druids Grove</a><font color=#333399> - </font><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgroverants>Rants</a> <font color=#333399> - </font><a href="http://www.thedruidsgrove.org">The Druids Grove</a><font color=#333399> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 6.9.4.8<br>Copyright ©1999-2002 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  

